{"tid":2217912,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–不會變啡的白蘑菇","createTime":"2020-09-25T20:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T23:46:31.000Z","uid":38861,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb5a51e5ce5589d54f6ffca7c8dfead5096e819","tid":2217912,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T20:55:05.000Z","msg":"上集提及了白蘑菇表面的啡點是由Brown Blotch Disease而起，今集將會講及白蘑菇因為氧化作用而變成啡色的過程。<br />\n<br />\n上集：<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/486079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F486079&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=e7d8715c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/486079</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aHB6yn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aHB6yn.jpg&h=f4c54699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAgGydq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAgGydq.png&h=dbc27cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）正常情況下，名為PPO的酵素將會處於名為Plastid的位置內，與蘑菇裡頭的Phenolic Substrate天隔一方，河水不犯井水。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/broYArO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbroYArO.jpg&h=e40071c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）而在物理性的撞擊或其他作用底下，Plastid結構被受破壞，PPO酵素便與蘑菇裡頭的Phenolic Substrate接觸，透過氧氣的協助下產生一系列的化學反應，最終形成啡黑色物質Melanin，導致白蘑菇變成啡蘑菇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZS9Qryx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZS9Qryx.jpg&h=f57b5a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）白蘑菇因氧化作用而變成啡色並不會讓蘑菇變成不得食用。<br />\n移居到美國賓夕法尼亞州立大學的中國科學家Yinong Yang已成功使用CRISPR基因編輯技術將蘑菇的PPO基因剔走，製作不會變啡的白蘑菇，主要為作美觀用途。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TmPT8MZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTmPT8MZ.jpg&h=46c57746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCRISPR技術延伸閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/465369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F465369&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=c10b5703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/465369</a><br />\n<br />\n只要得到法律的允許，這些不會變啡的白蘑菇便能進入商業市場。<br />\n<br />\n類近的基因改造產品，已投身市場標榜不會變啡的蘋果Acratic Apple，原理同樣亦是針對PPO基因而成，但箇中並沒有用上CRISPR手段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=89b5289e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=cdb169e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。"},{"pid":"5cc44f5c51c984950d0ded8e8999d4abac3d98cd","tid":2217912,"uid":209079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T20:56:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ef1ffaaa7bdfb9341adb06cc5a2b157c44b5edbd","tid":2217912,"uid":3037,"like":1,"d